# Recollect AI Journal - Support

Welcome to the Recollect AI Journal support page. We’re here to help you get the most out of your journaling experience.

## Frequently Asked Questions

### 1. How do I create a new journal entry?
To create a new entry, simply tap the "+" button on the main screen. You can add text, images, and more to customize each entry.

### 2. How do I back up my journal?
Your entries are saved securely within the app, but it’s recommended to back them up to your iCloud or Google Drive. Go to **Settings > Backup** to start.

### 3. Can I password protect my journal?
Yes! You can enable password protection by going to **Settings > Security**.

## Need Further Help?
